high_descs: Turn left, go to the side of the coffee table, turn right to face the coffee table.
Take the keys from the coffee table.
Turn around and face the seat on the left.
Put the keys on the seat cushion.
Turn left, go to the round black table next to the seat.
Take the keys from the table.
Go to the seat next to the round black table.
Put the keys on the seat cushion to the right of the other keys.
anns.task_desc: Put keys on a seat's cushion.

high_descs: Turn left and begin walking across the room, stop at the coffee table and turn right.
Pick up the keys off of the black coffee table.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right again to face the chair.
Place the keys on the seat of the chair.
Turn left and begin walking towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the small round table.
Pick up the keys off of the small round table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk over to the closest chair with the keys on the seat.
Place the keys you are holding on the chair seat to the right of the keys that are already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys onto a chair seat.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the closest short side of the table.
Pick up the key chain on the table.
Turn around and walk left to the chair.
Put the key chain on the chair.
Walk left to the night stand.
Pick up the key chain on the stand.
Step right to the chair.
Place the keys on the chair to the right of the other chair.
anns.task_desc: Place two key chains on a chair.
